# GPRTool -- Project Brief

## What this is
GPRTool is a web-based 3D visualisation and analysis application, likely for Green Plot Ratio calculations, developed by Boon Ong/Curtin University. It primarily uses HTML/CSS/JavaScript with Three.js for 3D rendering, and ES modules for structure. There are archived Python backend components. Deployment is implied to be web-based, possibly via Vercel.

## Deployment
